"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024716","Department for Transport","false","2018-12-18","<p>In general terms, my Department would not expect there to be a major effect on the Port of Liverpool of leaving the EU without a deal, nor therefore, through such impacts, on the regional or national economy.</p>","Epsom and Ewell","Chris Grayling","202065 ; 202066","2018-12-18T12:06:40.857Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024716/answer","Biography information for Chris Grayling","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024716/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024716/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2018-12-13","Liverpool Port","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what assessment he has made of the potential effect of the UK leaving the EU without a deal on the port of Liverpool and its subsequent effect on (a) national and (b) regional economies.","false","Biography information for Luciana Berger","Liverpool, Wavertree","Luciana Berger","202064"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024717","Department for Transport","false","2018-12-18","<p>In general terms, my Department would not expect there to be a major effect on the Port of Liverpool of leaving the EU without a deal, nor therefore, through such impacts, on the regional or national economy.</p>","Epsom and Ewell","Chris Grayling","202064 ; 202066","2018-12-18T12:06:40.92Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024717/answer","Biography information for Chris Grayling","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024717/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1024717/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2018-12-13","Liverpool Port","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what assessment he has made of the potential effect on levels of employment at the port of Liverpool in the event that the UK leaves the EU without a deal.","false","Biography information for Luciana Berger","Liverpool, Wavertree","Luciana Berger","202065"
